latestPosts.caption:
#notsponsored reviews👇🏼💞 

🔆 @reachedmars zero blend foundation (My shade 06): I loved how it blended onto my skin, but after 2-3 hours I did start cracking up in few areas and looked slightly cakey, so I am not sure about this foundation. 
 
🐻 @faebeautyofficial liquid blush (My shade: Silly): I do really like the formula, the blendability, this shade specifically. I think it’s a good alternative for the Huda beauty’s viral blonzing blush in latte. 

💜 @nykaacosmetics super light mascara: I had no plans of even trying this but I did for this video and I have to say I was proved wrong. It did take 4-5 coats to get me this lash because I have very small lashes, but it is a good mascara. Do like it

🤎 @faebeautyofficial re-define lip liners: I bought 4 shades from them and I only like 2 of them. The shade range is quite disappointing. First of all none of shades match the colour at the bottom of the pencil. They colour at the bottom looks so pretty and tempting but once you see what’s inside, I didn’t really like it. Only 2 shades I like are Bottomline and Hardline 

💞 @typebeautyinc Lip lustres with SPF35 No surprise here I just love the lip gloss. They have 2 variants with 2 shades each. The orange cap is for dry and dehydrated lips and the pink cap is for pigmented lips. 

.
